  PART 2: WHAT'S MISSING/INCOMPLETE ⚠️

  CRITICAL GAPS (Must Fix Before Production)

  1. Environment & Configuration Management (Critical)

  Issues:
  - ❌ No secrets management solution (AWS Secrets Manager, Vault, etc.)
  - ❌ .env.example contains placeholder values but no validation at runtime
  - ❌ No config validation on startup (app will fail at runtime instead of
  startup)
  - ❌ Missing production environment configuration guide

  Impact: App may start with invalid config and fail in production.

  Recommendation:
  // Add config validation at startup
  function validateConfig() {
    const required = ['DATABASE_URL', 'JWT_SECRET', 'JWT_REFRESH_SECRET'];
    const missing = required.filter(key => !process.env[key]);
    if (missing.length > 0) {
      throw new Error(`Missing required env vars: ${missing.join(', ')}`);
    }
    // Add length checks for JWT secrets
    if (process.env.JWT_SECRET!.length < 32) {
      throw new Error('JWT_SECRET must be at least 32 characters');
    }
  }

